parameters:
Yeah... It seems like I was sent to a different
place.
I see... I was worried about you.
I'm sorry. But nothing happened, so it's okay.

You're safe because you were sent with me. We've
already returned to the room.

Well then, I guess that's it for today. Shall we
go back to the room?
We'll continue the exploration tomorrow, right?
I hope everything really is okay.

(I'll trust Amelia... but for some reason, I have
a bad feeling)

Hoffman's class... I have to protect Amelia as
much as possible.

But I wonder if Amelia is really okay... Just to
be safe, I should also check with the Dark
Purchase Club.
